Piranha - Project 20.9.0 API

The Piranha Project delivers you with Cloud ready containers and useful add-on / integration modules.

The following distributions are available.

  1. Piranha Nano
  2. Piranha Embedded
  3. Piranha Micro
  4. Piranha Server
